{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980426+00:00", "phase": "handoff", "from": "security", "to": "gtm", "message": "GTM should explicitly leverage the gating of critical security features like SAML SSO, SCIM, and audit logs as a primary upsell driver from Business to Enterprise plans."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980826+00:00", "phase": "handoff", "from": "gtm", "to": "marketing", "message": "Marketing must partner with the new GTM Operations function to produce the quantitative ROI case studies needed to support the enterprise consolidation pitch, addressing a key content gap."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980875+00:00", "phase": "handoff", "from": "marketing", "to": "security", "message": "Security must be advised that our 'tool consolidation' value proposition makes Notion a high-value target, requiring a specific incident response plan for a wide blast radius breach."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980906+00:00", "phase": "handoff", "from": "security", "to": "finance", "message": "Finance should model the potential compliance liability stemming from non-Enterprise customer data being retained by undisclosed third-party AI vendors."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980934+00:00", "phase": "synergy", "depts": ["gtm", "security", "marketing"], "text": "Notion's enterprise sales motion is fundamentally powered by its security model; it deliberately paywalls critical compliance and governance features to create a high-stakes, non-negotiable upsell path for large customers."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980963+00:00", "phase": "synergy", "depts": ["gtm", "security", "marketing"], "text": "Notion's primary growth strategy around AI automation introduces an unquantified fourth-party risk by processing customer data through undisclosed third-party LLMs, creating a compliance and trust liability for all but its top-tier Enterprise clients who are guaranteed zero data retention."}
{"t": "2026-05-28T10:54:51.980994+00:00", "phase": "synergy", "depts": ["marketing", "security", "gtm"], "text": "By successfully positioning itself as the central nervous system that consolidates a company's tools, Notion simultaneously makes itself a 'single point of catastrophic failure' where the impact of a breach is magnified across all connected systems."}
